Class AbstractAutoServiceMock

This is the generic abstract mock service. It is called with references to the actual service and the associated mock ReST service and provides a proxy reference to both. This enables component unit tests to only create this mock service and not have to know about how the actual services and their mock ReST services are created. The flags from the ReST service is intercepted here and passed through.
